        "cooked": "<p>Having Group Chat Conversation in a different section to 1:1 conversation section, and the ability to be able to name group chats like in Whatsapp.</p>\n<p>I have attached a screenshot, and it shows what I mean by having having Group Chat Conversation in a different section to 1:1 conversation, so Group Chat Conversation could be in rooms section</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2_2_690x354.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"kKEnpZjtyH8au84OQiVzr3mp8xs\" width=\"690\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2_2_690x354.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2_2_1035x531.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/91717ca3ffeedb6a3c761ca2341c53003752c1b2_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1124×577 23.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
