        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/90ced4/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-04-17T15:04:38.445Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The messages screen could be improved with 2 tabs, one for direct messages and another for groups.</p>\n<p>Each tabs header would have an indicator of how many unread conversations exist and the tab with the most recent message would get the focus when someone opens the app.</p>\n<p>Users would possible swipe left or right to change between the tabs.</p>\n<p>This, I think, would provide less visual clutter. Additionally, each tab could have an indicator for less technology savvy people to easily identify whether it is a group chat tab or individual chat tab.</p>",
