        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/noates/{size}/12742_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-05-12T09:01:04.866Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>Tabs for chats.</strong></p>\n<p>I would also like this feature implemented.</p>\n<p>I wouldn’t suggesting adding to or overcrowding the UI at all, but including a customisable tab section above the message list (as used in telegram - see below) would make managing chats much easier…</p>\n<p>For those like yourself, with supposedly no need for tabs, the default (far left) tab is always “All” in telegram, so the same list of chats as you would see normally. To make sure this doesn’t prove an issue for those who <em>really</em> don’t want the feature, why not disable tabs completely unless tabs are set up?</p>\n<p>I find organising chats into group chats / family / friends one of the most useful unique features that some chat apps have now started to implement. I suggest and urge Signal to do the same ASAP!</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28\" title=\"signal-2021-05-12-095300\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28_2_230x500.jpeg\" alt=\"signal-2021-05-12-095300\" data-base62-sha1=\"fYAvVZXkZATiJNzYhS3OyB74vLq\" width=\"230\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28_2_230x500.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28_2_345x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28_2_460x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/6/f/6ff9f3415e588aafa586dff8fc63ae5675fecb28_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-ico